==English==

===Etymology===
Multiple origins, the popularity of the word spread through the internet.
* A portmanteau of [[fool]] and [[boob]]
* A portmanteau of [[fucking]] and [[noob]] (though use is not vulgar)

===Noun===
'''foob''', '''f00b''', '''F))B''' 
